      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHOW ON THE ROAD (3) held on to score in a photo finish last start when jumping the favourite at this trip at Ascot. This looks to shape similarly with Parnham remaining in the saddle. Should be in a prominent position from the outset and will be tough to reel in once more. JAVELIN STRIKE (2) won well two back before a 0.7L defeat most recently at Ascot. The better draw this time should see him closer to the speed and he looks to be hitting his straps now. Can get back to winning ways. FLAMING RONDA (7) finished 3L off the winner last start at Northam but was in better touch prior at Ascot. Out to the mile for the first time now and that looks a big tick for her chances. Up to the mile now looks a big tick and she can feature in the finish. CAPE LEEUWIN (1) can improve third-up and getting out to this trip for the first time. ALABRAE (5) just missed two back over this trip and a return to that form would see him go close.",
